node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Crusoe the Dachshund on July 28, 2021. May be an image of dog and grass.

node.text: UPDATE: Crusoe just had his first blood test in 3 months (longest gap between tests since all this started), and we are very very happy to say his liver enzymes remain normal and stable.. 🥰 It’s hard to believe that just 6 months ago they were 15x normal and he was going into a 2nd tough, scary surgery.. So, we could NOT be more appreciative and thankful that this turned out better than we ever hoped.. and for that, we remind ourselves every single day how special Crusoe is to us.❤️” ~ Crusoe
